Dump stats to file

tiledb_stats_dump.Rd

Dump stats to file

tiledb_stats_dump(path)

Arguments

path

to stats file

Examples

pth <- tempfile()
tiledb_stats_dump(pth)
cat(readLines(pth)[1:10], sep = "\n")
#> ===================================== TileDB Statistics Report =======================================
#> 
#> Individual function statistics:
#>   Function name                                                          # calls       Total time (ns)
#>   ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#>   compressor_bzip_compress,                                                    0,                   0
#>   compressor_bzip_decompress,                                                  0,                   0
#>   compressor_dd_compress,                                                      0,                   0
#>   compressor_dd_decompress,                                                    0,                   0
#>   compressor_gzip_compress,                                                    0,                   0
